---
title: Projects
description: These are a few of the projects I've made, but there are many more.
layout: primary
pageName: projectsPage
addCSS: true
addJS: true
---
<main class="layout">
  <header class="page-header center">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1><span id="proj-title">{{ title }}</span></h1>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="projects__focus">

    {%- projectFeature 'Front Royal (The Band, Not The Town)', 'fr' -%}
      <section class="project-image">
        {%- screenshot 'https://www.frontroyalband.com', 'front-royal', 'Screenshot of the Front Royal website' -%}
      </section>
      <section class="project-description">
        <p>When we decided to take the plunge and have a website of our own, I signed myself up to make it. It gave me the opportunity to try some new things out and I'm proud of the result.</p>
        <p class="details">Built With: Eleventy.</p>
      </section>
    {%- endprojectFeature -%}

    {%- projectFeature 'NotSocial: A New Type of Social Media', 'ns' -%}
      <section class="project-image">
        {%- screenshot 'https://www.notsocial.app/', 'notsocial', 'Screenshot of the NotSocial website' -%}
      </section>
      <section class="project-description">
        <p>You ever wish you had a social media platform that didn't consume your life, but still gave you entertainment? Look no further than NotSocial.</p>
        <p class="details">Built With: Nuxt.</p>
      </section>
    {%- endprojectFeature -%}

    {%- projectFeature 'An Abandoned Website', 'aw' -%}
      <section class="project-image">
        {%- screenshot 'https://www.abandoned.website', 'abandoned-website', 'Screenshot of the Abandoned Website homepage' -%}
      </section>
      <section class="project-description">
        <p>What if a website, left to wither away and be forgotten, actually looked abandoned over time?</p>
        <p class="details">Built With: Hugo.</p>
      </section>
    {%- endprojectFeature -%}

    {%- projectFeature 'troy. is a band', 'tr' -%}
      <section class="project-image">
        <a href="https://validcharacters.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="/assets/img/validcharacters1920x1080.jpeg" alt="Screenshot of the troy homepage" width="320" height="180" loading="lazy"/>
        </a>
      </section>
      <section class="project-description">
        <p>i decided to give troy. - a band I have - a website. while i don't do anything serious with the band, it was fun to make something.</p>
        <p class="details">built with: eleventy.</p>
      </section>
    {%- endprojectFeature -%}

  </section>
  <section class="codepen">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h3>View More on CodePen</h3>
      <p>I've made a lot of things - bigger and smaller - that would be impossible to keep track of on here. From experimenting with JavaScript frameworks, to making things animate for no good reason, to even coding emails (yikes!). You could say I'm winging it over there.</p>
      {% button 'https://codepen.io/troyvassalotti', 'See My CodePen' %}
    </div>
  </section>
